{"tid":1534735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人用無人機阻止飛機升降","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T07:10:32.000Z","uid":211270,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5428ea44638465f6111cb9d658f236405c4920ab","tid":1534735,"uid":211270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:59:06.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】英國有環保組織周四（29日）宣布將於9月13日，利用小型無人機癱瘓倫敦希斯路機場。環保人士稱希望藉阻止航班升降向政府施壓，迫使政府採更強硬措施減少碳排放。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n環保組織「The Heathrow Pause」稱當天會在機場附近的5公里受管制範圍內放飛無人機，雖不會飛入機場的航機飛行路線，無人機飛行高度亦不會比人高，但該組織稱足以阻止航班升降，又會在行動前1小時通知機場。<br />\n<br />\n見到篇新聞幾有趣，同大家分享吓，絕對唔鼓勵大家咁樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f96b6d90aae6b3c8442fb11b083a3a94441eb9","tid":1534735,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75fa6abb9d285f8e61074c1fdeadc05e07ebb95f","tid":1534735,"uid":211270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33f96b6d90aae6b3c8442fb11b083a3a94441